{"sta":1,"data":{"subTitle":"输入框的布局","content":"<p>我们常常需要在输入框的前方添加提示，后方添加按钮。<a href=\"/app/data/css3/flex/case/input.html\" target=\"_blank\">查看Demo</a></p><p><img src=\"/app/data/css3/flex/img/bg2015071324.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p>HTML代码如下。</p><pre><code>\n<span><span><span>&lt;</span>div</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>InputAddOn<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>span</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>InputAddOn-item<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>...<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>span</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>input</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>InputAddOn-field<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>button</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>InputAddOn-item<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>...<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>button</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre><p>CSS代码如下。</p><pre><code>\n<span>.InputAddOn </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>display</span><span>:</span> flex<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.InputAddOn-field </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>flex</span><span>:</span> 1<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span></code></pre>"}}